bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/c9705b528b14205658936071e37ae618.poster.avif?t=1728903451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/c9705b528b14205658936071e37ae618.webm?t=1728903451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/c9705b528b14205658936071e37ae618.mp4?t=1728903451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Host Game:<br>Set your card game format and fee, invite players to play card games in your shop. Be sure to keep your store clean and hygienic for the players or they might leave!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.poster.avif?t=1728903451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.webm?t=1728903451\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/153eb4e293d32b366ea38984e8dec12c.mp4?t=1728903451\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Order Products:<br>Stock up on different booster card packs and card game products. Keep track of popular trends and adjust your inventory to cater to the ever-changing demands of your customers.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/5c4e1fbe14e8db61d596a6f0639f8ad6.poster.avif?t=1728903451\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083940/extras/5c4e1fbe14e8db61d596a6f0639f8ad6.webm?t=172890